        "余勇可贾。"
      ],
      "traditional_char": "賈"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "part_of_speech": "verb",
      "meaning": "买，购买",
      "examples": [
        "平子每岁贾马。",
        "贾余馀勇。"
      ],
      "traditional_char": "賈"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "part_of_speech": "verb",
      "meaning": "谋求，求取（如名利等）",
      "examples": [
        "谋于众不以贾好。",
        "贾誉（沽名钓誉）"
      ],
      "traditional_char": "賈"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "part_of_speech": "verb",
      "meaning": "招引，招致",
      "examples": [
        "吾焉用此以贾害也。",
        "不怀宝以贾害。"
      ],
      "traditional_char": "賈"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "part_of_speech": "noun",
      "meaning": "古官名，管理市场商业的官",
      "examples": [
        "贾正（古官名）",
        "郈鲂假使为贾正焉。"
      ],
      "traditional_char": "賈"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "part_of_speech": "noun",
      "meaning": "价格，价值（通“价”）",
      "examples": [
